{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>人員接報到場，47歲姓陳男子現場被證實死亡。據了解，他生前患有身體疾病。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/5501087/org/ec25cc4f4da462b530956c6bfef403f3.jpg/uY9-jLeFhHBoUyrACs1f4Mq2RH6mYn9JkbvewIu73sA\" alt=\"油麻地警署。（蔡正邦攝/資料圖片）\"><figcaption>油麻地警署。（蔡正邦攝/資料圖片）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-28T05:34:07.390416+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":54,"images":1,"source":"HK01 突發","fallback":"none"}}